Install of Metadata for python 2.7

pip install pyacoustid: # Used for Acoustid API, which gets the metadata

Download ffmpeg: from https://www.ffmpeg.org/ as tar.gz # ffmpeg is used to record the music

Install yasm: Sudo apt-get install yasm. This is in order to install ffmpeg

Extract and cd into ffmpeg

Configure, make and install ffmpeg via ./configure && make && install

sudo apt-get install libchromaprint-tools # this installs ChromaPrint for audio fingerprinting
